<translate>
<!--T:1-->
'''Holiday Event 2025''' is a community event to celebrate the [[Wikipedia:Christmas_and_holiday_season|Christmas and holiday season]] for 2025. The event features a winter themed [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|Shop]] content, a gifting campaign and several rewards for users participating. It takes place from December 8, 2025 - January 1, 2026.

==Holiday Event== <!--T:2--></translate>
[[File:HolidayEvent2025 VRC+Page.png|thumb|<translate><!--T:3--> Holiday Event 2025 Menu Screenshot</translate>]]
<translate><!--T:22--> The Holiday Event is a community gifting campaign for the holiday season.</translate>

<translate><!--T:4--> Users can participate and track progress by navigating to the Holiday Event tab in the VRC+ page on the Main Menu. By participating in the campaign, users earn several rewards, such as exclusive inventory content and a badge for completing the event.</translate>

<translate><!--T:5--> The campaign began at 11:40PM UTC on December 8th, 2025 and ends at 7:59:59AM UTC on January 1st, 2026.</translate>

<translate>===Leaderboards=== <!--T:6--></translate>
<translate><!--T:7--> Users that have participated in the event by gifting can appear on the top gifters leaderboard. The "2025 Holiday Heros" leaderboard section is spilt up between global and friends. Both lists will show the top 10 gifters, and the top three users will have different stages of holiday wreaths applied to their profile picture.</translate>

<translate><!--T:8--> Users can choose to "Appear as Anonymous" to anonymize their username appearing on the global and friends list.</translate>

<translate>===Rewards=== <!--T:9--></translate>
<translate><!--T:10--> The following rewards can be obtained from this event:</translate>

<translate><!--T:11-->
* Festive Starter Pack
** Available to everyone
** "[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|Festive Starter Pack]]" bundle</translate>

<translate><!--T:12-->
* The First Gift
** Available to users who gifted one VRC+ subscription or Shop gift.</translate><ref name="CreditsPurchase" group="note"><translate><!--T:21--> Purchasing VRChat Credits counts towards gift count.</translate></ref>
** <translate><!--T:24--> "[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|Tree-in-a-Box]]" Premium [[Special:MyLanguage/Emojis|emoji]]</translate>

<translate><!--T:13-->
* VRC+ Gifter
** Available to users who gifted one VRC+ subscription.</translate><ref name="CreditsPurchase" group="note" />
** <translate><!--T:23--> "[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|VRC+ Gifter]]" bundle</translate>

<translate><!--T:14-->
* Holiday Legend
** Available to users who gifted five VRC+ subscriptions or Shop gifts.<ref name="CreditsPurchase" group="note" />
** "Wrapped Up!" [[Special:MyLanguage/Warp Effects|warp effect]]</translate>

[[File:Prop-SnowBlaster-Image-2022322f1.file 1e2ee01b-b9fa-4c19-b14d-b2f701a295cd.3.webp|right|thumb]]
<translate><!--T:15-->
* Community Spirit Reward
** Available to everyone after reaching the gifting goal of 200,000 gifts given.</translate><ref name="gifts" group="note"><translate><!--T:26--> Gifting shop items, avatars, world store listings and VRC+ subscriptions all count toward the tracker. </translate></ref>
<translate><!--T:27--> ** "Winter Cheerizer" [[Special:MyLanguage/Items|item]]</translate>

<translate><!--T:16-->
* Keeper of the Spirit
** Available to users who claimed the "Festive Starter Pack", "The First Gift", "VRC+ Gifter", and "Holiday Legend" rewards.
** "Keeper of the Spirit" [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|badge]]</translate>

<references group="note" />

